description: Bring that unmistakeable coffeehouse vibe to your home (or coffeehouse!) with the help of this laidback acoustic covers selection. Featuring stunning stripped-down versions of well-known songs, it's the perfect background music soundtrack to any latte, americano, cappucino, mocha or espresso!
